channel.title: Help with 562 loading 604 cache
channel.description:
[size=12pt]i recently downloaded TkoScape. The client that came with it is a 562 loading 604 cache. When I try to rum the client, it freezes at 4% them eventually displays the Js5connect error. I'm wondering if theirs another client i'm able to use or if someone would be able to help me. Thanks :)
[/size]

item.title: Help with 562 loading 604 cache
item.dc:creator: @tarheels tarheels
item.description:
@tarheels wrote:

Wildyscape562:

Its not finding your ipaddress, see if anyone else can connect to it and if so then you need to change the ip address for yourself only to 127.0.0.1

Everyone can connect, or at least the source’s prompt detects a connection. But the client has the same error for everyone too.
